metadata.name: Gone. Too Soon :)
metadata.description:
#1

She looks down from the heavens at the man who was once her beloved. 

He's in the embrace of someone else now. Is it love?



Lana Del Rey inspires me like almost no one else.

This first piece and a few other pieces in this collection are therefore going to have her as my muse. Call it love, call it an homage or call it a tribute.
